  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9 \u0d85\u0dbb\u0db9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Work begins in the President's office",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Work will start today only 11 days after the presidential office was liberated from the militants.",
        "Work at the officer level of the President's Office is also scheduled to begin. Within a short period of time, the President is also scheduled to start work from the President's Office.",
        "Sources in the President's Office state that the renovation works are already underway at the President's Office."
      ],
